                                <div>
                                    <p>
                                    Apply now for a Fidem Mastercard Card as a next step on your road to financial improvement.     
                                    Once your application is approved, the Fidem Mastercard card provides you with:
                                        <ul style="margin: 0; list-style-type: none;">
                                            <li class = "blackBullet">True credit – no security deposit required</li>
                                            <li class = "blackBullet">A Credit limit up to $3,000</li>
                                            <li class = "blackBullet">Use it anywhere Mastercard Cards are accepted</li>
                                            <li class = "blackBullet">Online access to your Card account</li>
                                            <li class = "blackBullet">Minimum monthly amount – the greater of $30 or 4%</li>
                                            <li class = "blackBullet">Reports to credit bureaus every month under Fidem Card/BC</li>
                                        </ul></p>
                               </div>
                                <p>The application should take only <b> 5-10 minutes to complete,</b> and you'll receive a response in as little as 30 seconds.</p>
                                
                                
